       <H3 class="section_header"> Ceremony/Reception </H3>

<p class="section_body">Our ceremony will begin at 4 pm on Saturday, September 20th

 with the reception (Drinks! Dinner! Dancing!) 

immediately following. The ceremony and reception will 

both take place outdoors. Our wedding was inspired by 

Miranda’s two great loves (after Brandon, of course): 

France in general and Paris in the 1920s in particular. 

We’ll have plenty of pastries and desserts on hand to 

satisfy your sweet tooth, as well as a selection of vintage 

cocktails to get you feeling hotsy-totsy!

</p>


<p class="section_body"><i>Brandon and Miranda respectfully request that this be an 

adults-only affair. If you will need childcare, please don’t 

hesitate to call us! Miranda (970) 217-6419 or Brandon (303) 

550-2844.</i></p>

<p class="section_body">

