</p>

<H3 class="section_header">Honeymoon</H3>

<p class="section_body">Two days after the wedding, we’ll be embarking on a 

European adventure with stops in Munich, Salzburg, 

Vienna, and Prague. First up: Oktoberfest! This trip will 

be extra special because we’ve invited our siblings to join 

us. Since we all live in different states and our schedules 

don’t permit us to visit as often as we’d like, we decided 

this would be the perfect opportunity for us to spend some 

quality time together.</p>

